title: Alpine heading for Japan!
text: Some members of the team are already familiar with Fuji Speedway, but this will be the Alpine A450bs first attempt at the Vincent Capillaire: Theres a good rhythm to the calendar now. We know our strengths and we know what we need to deliver to come away from Japan with a strong result. We just need to convert our progress into a podium finish.
